{"tid":1532091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急!!! 急需一D手足唔好洗螢光粉！做實驗！！！","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:49.000Z","uid":189739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6709f4413fab02f797fa2f44faa883d24f05092f","tid":1532091,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"急需手足幫忙做實驗拆螢光粉<br />\n1. 用水洗唔水得甩，洗得甩好易搞<br />\n2. 洗唔甩幫我做呢個實驗：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用防曬！！</span></span><br />\n防曬可以吸紫外光，我試左如果用在鈔票，有效！！<br />\n<br />\nBefore<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hfgiiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hfgiiY.jpg&h=1e4ca2d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAfter<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHADwD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHADwD5.jpg&h=7ecb1859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n防曬對隱形墨水唔work, 可能係隱形墨水既螢光劑既excitation spectra同防曬absorption spectra唔同, 所以要你地幫手試！<br />\n<br />\n如果係難洗既話，而防曬係work，可以用來做緊急處理"},{"pid":"1dc40be4cc90f33d8b2cfe764013dafb66e45135","tid":1532091,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03e75327ae45fd84fd070f886b291739741e34f9","tid":1532091,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddbecb43a1fab2ab1b2d999bdfe16afd47626b8","tid":1532091,"uid":216966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d0c93c2129a114dcf4d5b4551917b81045d0bef7","tid":1532091,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b5cc575b40b19f80b6432f75113f7d0259b306b7","tid":15320